description.en:
Stakenet is a Lightning Network-ready open-source platform for decentralized applications (dApps) with its native cryptocurrency – XSN. It is the first blockchain with Masternodes to be Lightning Network ready. XSN has instant, virtually feeless, and unlimited transactions per second, and has the first Lightning Network DEX running on its network. XSN is the first, next to Bitcoin and Litecoin, to ever perform Lightning Swaps.

XSN is digital money, like bitcoin in the Bitcoin blockchain, or ether in Ethereum, as its supply is not controlled by any government or company. With Stakenet’s Trustless Proof of Stake, users can stake their coins from cold storage (such as a hardware wallet) and receive staking rewards whilst their funds are offline and not at risk - with the goal of offering strong security

status_updates.description:
We are proud to announce we are now a member of Square's Crypto Open Patent Alliance, COPA.

We join fellow members Coinbase, Kraken, Blockstream, Satoshi Labs and 13 other members to take a stand against the threat of patent abuse in this industry:

https://medium.com/stakenet/stakenet-joins-squares-crypto-open-patent-alliance-copa-211b311324b0

As our Lightning DEX transitions from Stage 1 to Stage 2 "Prometheus", our team has prepared initial architecture for the upcoming Stage 3 "Hydra" network upgrade.

Check out below for details on fee structure, distribution & the role of Masternodes:

https://medium.com/stakenet/hydra-dex-network-upgrade-proposal-4b00a3a3fb8

Stakenet (XSN) has been listed on Bitfinex!

Bitfinex is a top exchange with a focus on adopting Lightning Network and Layer 2 technologies making them an obvious choice for XSN  as it is tightly aligned with our vision of where we see the future going. 

We are excited for the future to come as we both push LN and  L2 scaling to the masses! 

Read more about the listing and a celebration giveaway in our medium article here:

https://bit.ly/2XvFKKH

XSN Dev update is now live. Check out the link below for info on:

- BTC<>USDT integration via Lightning Network and Connext.
- Wallet and DEX updates including a redesign and Ethereum + ERC20 support.
- New exchanges and partnerships like DuckDAO

And much more on the link below:

https://medium.com/stakenet/xsn-core-update-jan-2021-1f2b1f585b58

On our way to the DEX public launch, we are thrilled to announce our partnership with DuckDAO, a digital asset incubator that provides hand selected crypto projects with expertise, financial resources, and marketing power needed to fast track their progress on the path to success.

Stakenet plans to work with DuckDAO as a Liquidity Provider for the DEX as well as marketing and community support.

Read all about below:
https://medium.com/duckdao/duckdao-stakenet-xsn-partnership-4a2a6e077aeb

We are happy to announce our partnership with ARK and MarketSquare on building community together and exploring blockchain developments. Read all about it on the link below:

https://ark.io/blog/ark-announces-partnership-with-stakenet

Stakenet (XSN) has just listed on WhiteBIT and Felixo, to read all about it and the pairings head on over to the link below:
https://medium.com/stakenet/exchange-listing-announcement-dec-31-2020-9a2f3727fb4f
